{"tid":891101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「拜託你不要停」退休女師車震　富商行車紀錄器揭腥情","createTime":"2018-11-05T23:52:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T02:55:10.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"96268b9a5a6893b6ad267c1eabed9192dfd3e3f8","tid":891101,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T23:52:29.000Z","msg":"40年之癢！赫然發現老公入住摩鐵的發票，再查行車紀錄器，嬌嗔淫聲全都錄。<br />\n今日出版的《自由時報》報導，新北市通訊器材、電腦設備公司的蔡姓負責人，與結婚40年的妻子一同經營公司。2016年，蔡妻發現老公入住新北市一家摩鐵的發票，還查出他帶著1名黃姓退休女老師出遊多次，甚至在車子的行車紀錄器發現2人對話、呻吟聲和喘息聲等，黃女嗲聲嗲氣說「拜託你不要停」、「我以為你太興奮刺激了」等，告上法院。<br />\n蔡男與黃女否認有不正常關係，蔡稱因年紀大，開車累了才會到摩鐵休息。高等法院認為，雖無法證明兩人有通姦事證，但車內肢體「親密接觸」，研判有不當交往，判應連帶賠償蔡妻40萬元確定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181106/1460989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181106%2F1460989&d=eG%2BH%2BmnwJydb3jju8aYqiQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=81f2caf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20181106%2F1460989&h=5faadbce\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20181106/1460989</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fe61c24fc279068c0e098b5c71fa1763bc056a","tid":891101,"uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T23:58:49.000Z","msg":"退休女教師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97bfc1630162c0cde9495911b19a8d35bbec1a9","tid":891101,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:04:32.000Z","msg":"車速快姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d6bcb6baf1259b4d8421cb647e528b1a959a2a","tid":891101,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T00:24:29.000Z","msg":"新北市又入一球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src